petition confident that I was going to be able to hit for the team.\\\"\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that competition\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone also gave insight into their group huddle done after every event, which serves as a team reminder to stay in their \\\"bubble\\\" in order to focus on their own performance versus the competition.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Malone\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"insight\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"their group huddle\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"every event\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"a team reminder\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"bubble\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"their own performance\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA's bronze is only their third team medal in 20 years, making it an emotional moment for the athletes, including Malone whose gymnastics career was almost over after a knee injury in 2023.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9922532160997976, \"rank\": 0.005104545469422726, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only their third team medal\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"whose gymnastics career\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"a knee injury\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You never really know how bad you want something until you get it taken away from you,\\\" Malone, 24, toldNBC2 Newsin Fort Myers, Florida, ahead of their big win.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1394, \"end\": 1413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Myers,_Florida\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fort Myers, Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Myers,_Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Myers,_Florida\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"their big win\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After competing in the Tokyo Olympics and not medaling, Malone set his sights on Paris.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"score\": 0.9979421838998328, \"rank\": 0.0015714164110111708, \"text\": \"Malone\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karl_Malone\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999972915248, \"rank\": 2.708260725058068e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phras