om\": 1756, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"his tibia\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His full diagnosis, according toTeam USA: a torn meniscus, tibial plateau fracture, partially torn posterior cruciate ligament and fully torn lateral collateral ligament.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His full diagnosis\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"USA\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"a torn meniscus\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"tibial plateau fracture\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"partially torn posterior cruciate ligament\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"fully torn lateral collateral ligament\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone underwent three surgeries, followed by weeks of bedrest and rehabbing for a year.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Malone\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"three surgeries\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2013}, {\"ngram\": \"bedrest\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"rehabbing\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone would go on to prove that he had made a comeback when he won his third U.S. title in Forth Worth, Texas, in June of this year.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Forth Worth, Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fort_Worth,_Texas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Forth Worth, Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q515